    a enum containing all modbus-function-codes listed in the modbus protocol v1.1b: 01 (0x01) Read Coils 02 (0x02) Read Discrete Inputs 03 (0x03) Read Holding Registers 04 (0x04) Read Input Registers 05 (0x05) Write Single Coil 06 (0x06) Write Single Register 07 (0x07) Read Exception Status (Serial Line only) 08 (0x08) Diagnostics (Serial Line only) 11 (0x0B) Get Comm Event Counter (Serial Line only) 12 (0x0C) Get Comm Event Log (Serial Line only) 15 (0x0F) Write Multiple Coils 16 (0x10) Write Multiple registers 17 (0x11) Report Slave ID (Serial Line only) 20 (0x14) Read File Record 21 (0x15) Write File Record 22 (0x16) Mask Write Register 23 (0x17) Read/Write Multiple registers 24 (0x18) Read FIFO Queue 43 ( 0x2B) Encapsulated Interface Transport 43 / 13 (0x2B / 0x0D) CAN open General Reference Request and Response PDU 43 / 14 (0x2B / 0x0E) Read Device Identification
